quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  29,26,"Basi Lutwi ŵankulupilile jwalakwe. (Ibrahima) ni jwatite: “Chisimu une ngusama wa kwa Ambuje ŵangu (Allah). Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka.”"
  29,27,"Ni twampele jwalakwe Isihaka ni Yaakubu, ni twaŵisile mu ŵanache ŵakwe utume ni chitabu, ni twampele malipilo gakwe pa duniya, soni chisimu jwalakwe ku Akhera tachiŵa mu ŵandu ŵambone"
  29,28,"Soni (munkumbuchilani) Lutwi pandema jajwatite ku ŵandu ŵakwe: “Chisimu ŵanganyammwe nkuiŵichilila yausakwa yanganannongoleleje ku (itenda) yalakweyo jwalijose mu iwumbe yosope.”"
  29,29,"“Ana chisimu ŵanganyammwe nkwaichilila achalume (pakwatenda matanyula), ni kutendaga ukachikwanje m’matala, ni kwikaga nayo itendo yangalumbana mu nganya syenu?” Basi ni nganiuŵa wanje wa ŵandu ŵakwe ikaŵeje ŵagambile kuti: “Ikani nayo kukwetu ilagasyo ya Allah, nam’baga n’di mwa akuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  29,30,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Munjenjelani ku ŵandu ŵakuwatanganya.”"
  29,31,"Sano katema kaŵaiche achimitenga Ŵetu kwa Ibrahima ni abali jakusengwasya ŵatite: “Chisimu uwwe chitwajonanje achinsyene awu musi (wa Sodomu), chisimu achinsyene ŵakwe aŵele ŵalupuso.”"
  29,32,"(Ibrahima) jwatite: “Chisimu mwalakwemo mwana Lutwi.” Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Uwwe tukwamanya chenene ŵali mwalakwemo. Chisimu uwwe chitun’jokole jwalakwe ni liŵasa lyakwe ikaŵeje ŵankwakwepe, chaŵe mwa akusigalila munyuma (chajonanjidwe).”"
  29,33,"Sano paŵagambile kum’bichilila Lutwi achimitenga Ŵetu, jwadandawile yaŵaganyao nikuŵanikwa nao chidali (pakwaajogopela kuti atakutendedwa matanyula, ni kusoŵa yakuti kaachenjele, ligongo nganiŵamanya kuti achimalaika). Ŵanganyao ni ŵatite: “Nkajogopa soni nkadandaula, chisimu uwwe chitun’jokole mmwe ni liŵasa lyenu ikaŵeje ŵankwenupe, chaŵe mwa akusigalila munyuma (chajonanjidwe).”"
  29,34,“Chisimu uwwe tusigele panandi kwatuluchisya achinsyene awu musi (wa Sodomu) ipotesi kutyochela kwinani ligongo lya kunyosya kwao.”
  29,35,Soni chisimu pamasile patwalesile mwalakwemo chimanyilo chakuonechela kwa ŵandu ŵaakwete lunda
  29,36,"Sano (kuŵandu ŵa) ku Madiyana (twantumisye) nnongo n’jao (jwali) Shuaibu. Basi jwatite: “E ŵandu ŵangu! Mun’galagatilani Allah, ni llijogope Lisiku Lyambesi, soni nkajendagajendaga pa chilambo kupita nchiwatanganya.”"
  29,37,"Ni ŵankaaniile, basi ni chakwembekenye chisikinya, mwanti ŵachelelwe (ali ŵawe) m’majumba mwao chitindiŵalile"
  29,38,"Nombe nao soni achina Adi ni achina Samuda (twajonasile), soni pamasile pakuonechele kukwenu (konasika kwao) kuumila m’malo mwao muŵatamaga (mwamusyuchile kuŵa m’masame). Soni shetani ni jwasalalichisye ŵanganyao itendo yao (yangalumbana), basi ni jwasiŵilile ŵanganyao kwitala (lyagoloka) namuno kuti ŵaliji ŵakulolechesya (pakutenda ichindu)"
  29,39,"Nombe najo soni Qaruna, Firiauna ni Hamana (twajonasile). Soni chisimu chene pamasile pajwaichilile ŵanganyao Musa ni isimosimo yakuonechela, basi ni ŵalikwesyisye pachilambo, kutendaga nganaŵa ŵanti ni kumpunda (Allah, mwanti ni kunnepelekasya kwapa ilagasyo)"
  29,40,"Basi jwalijose (mwa ŵanganyao) twankwembekenye ni sambi syakwe. Basi ŵane mwa jamanjao pana ŵatwatumichisye chimbunga cha sakalawe, ŵane mwa ŵanganyao pana ŵawakwembekenye n’gumilo (waipotesi), ŵane mwa ŵanganyao pana ŵatwatitimisye nalyo litaka, soni ŵane mwa ŵanganyao pana ŵatwamisyisye. Sano Allah nganijuŵa jwanti ni kwatenda lupuso ŵanganyao, nambo kuti ŵanyao ni ŵaŵaliji nkulitenda lupuso achimisyene"
  29,41,"Chilandanyo cha aŵala ŵalitendele jwinepe jwangaŵaga Allah kuŵa kaligoselo, chili chisawu nyangata jwalitendele nyumba (ja lundandambuli jangaŵa nkun’gosa kuchitukuta namuno mbepo), soni chisimu naga nyumba jangali machili ninyumba ja nyangata, ingaŵe ŵanganyao ŵamanyililaga"
  29,42,"Chisimu Allah jukuimanya ichindu iliyose yaakuilumbanjila ŵanganyao kunneka Jwalakwe, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  29,43,"Soni yalakweyo ni ilandanyo yatukupeleka ku ŵandu, ni ngakuitaga mu lunda ikaŵeje ŵakumanyililape"
  29,44,"Allah jwagumbile mawunde ni mataka mwakuonaonape, chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana chilosyo kwa ŵakulupilila"
  29,45,"Soomani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) yaijuwulidwe kukwenu ya m’Chitabu (cha Qur’an), ni n’jimicheje Swala mwakolosya, chisimu Swala jikasakanyaga yausakwa ni yangalumbana, soni kumbuchila kwa Allah (kwakunkumbuchila jenumanja pameso pa Achimalaika) ni kwakuli kwekulungwa nnope (kumpunda kumbuchila kwenu kwa kunkumbuchila Jwalakwe pa Swala syenu), soni Allah jukumanyilila yankupanganya"